  "description": "This individual is an undead of wasted build, their brown skin drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and a slack jaw that never fully closes. Gray eyes sit sunken and glassy beneath bruised lids, fixed in an unblinking stare that marks the loss of ordinary sensation. Black hair hangs in uneven, broken lengths, with bare patches where the scalp shows through in dull, healed scars. The hands are knotty and stiff, the fingers warped into a permanent curl typical of long unburied remains.",
